categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Kunpar was a male Jedi Master of the Jedi Order during the High Republic Era, stationed at the Valo Temple on the planet Valo. He was a member of a species that possessed chin tentacles. Prior to the opening of the Republic Fair on Valo, Jedi Padawan Ram Jomaram had slyly mentioned that one of the security team's speeder bikes was out of commission and that there were no mechanics available to fix it. Kunpar hesitantly allowed Jomaram to repair the vehicle in his garage instead of attending the fair preparations. The Master later accompanied Master Lege on advance preparations for the fair.
